OL,3,CIran's retaliation strikes leave Gulf
OL,4,CArab states fearing regional escalation
OL,6,FJohn Ray is in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia,
OL,7,Fwhere fears are growing of a regional
OL,8,Fescalation as Iran launches strikes on
OL,9,FGulf Arab states after its Supreme
OL,10,FLeader, Ali Khamenei, was killed in a
OL,11,FUS-Israel attack
OL,13,FThese are moments of high anxiety here
OL,14,Fin the Gulf, where they find
OL,15,Fthemselves in the firing line of a war
OL,16,Fthat was not of their choosing, and
OL,17,Fthe outcome of which they fear will
OL,18,Fdestabilise their region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
