CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772444181
OL,3,CIran's retaliation strikes leave Gulf
OL,4,CArab states fearing regional escalation
OL,6,FBut there is also widespread and
OL,7,Fgenuine anger at Iran's attacks on
OL,8,Ftheir territory; likely to intensify
OL,9,Fas the Revolutionary Guard threatens
OL,10,F''the most devastating operation in
OL,11,Fthe history of Iran'' in revenge for
OL,12,Fthe death of their Supreme Leader,
OL,13,FAyatollah Khamenei.
OL,15,FThis morning, there are again reports
OL,16,Fof fresh explosions in Bahrain, in
OL,17,FDubai and Doha.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
