OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772444181
OL,3,CIran's retaliation strikes leave Gulf
OL,4,CArab states fearing regional escalation
OL,6,FIran says the US's many military bases
OL,7,Fin the region are legitimate targets.
OL,8,FBut drones and missiles ` or at least
OL,9,Ffragments from intercepted attacks `
OL,10,Fhave damaged airports and hotels.
OL,12,FIran hopes that by attacking America's
OL,13,FArab friends, those allies will come
OL,14,Fto assert pressure on Washington to
OL,15,Fback down.
OL,17,FBut Tehran might have miscalculated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772444181
OL,3,CIran's retaliation strikes leave Gulf
OL,4,CArab states fearing regional escalation
OL,6,F''Iran has lost through this action
OL,7,Fthe sympathy that was pushing with
OL,8,Fevery possible effort towards de-
OL,9,Fescalation,'' wrote the former Emir of
OL,10,FQatar, Hamad Al Thani.
OL,12,FIn Bahrain, home to the US Navy's
OL,13,FFifth fleet, authorities call the
OL,14,Fattacks "treacherous" and "blatant
OL,15,Fviolations of the kingdom's
OL,16,Fsovereignty and security".
OL,18,FHere in Saudi Arabia, the foreign
OL,19,Fministry is reported to have repelled
OL,20,Fattacks on the capital, Riyadh and in
OL,21,Fterritory to the east.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772444181
OL,3,CIran's retaliation strikes leave Gulf
OL,4,CArab states fearing regional escalation
OL,6,FAfter the Saudis refused permission
OL,7,Ffor their airspace to be used in the
OL,8,Fattack on Iran, they said there can be
OL,9,Fno justification for the retaliation.
OL,11,FWhat unites the Gulf nations is a
OL,12,Fdesire for this war to end as soon as
OL,13,Fpossible, and a fear that it could get
OL,14,Fmuch worse.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
